SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES

Calculate Outcome Metrics Using Salesforce Flows (Pilot)

This feature is not generally available and is being piloted with certain Customers subject to additional terms and conditions. It is not part of your purchased Services. This feature is subject to change, may be discontinued with no notice at any time in Salesforce’s sole discretion.

Where: Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Health Cloud or Life Sciences Cloud license.

When: Patient Program Outcome Management available starting June 2024.

Who: Users with the Health Cloud Foundation (for Health Cloud) or Health Cloud Starter (for Life Sciences Cloud), and Patient Program Outcome Management permission set.

How: Create a flow with the process type Indicator Result Flow and associate it with an Indicator Definition record.
title: Calculate Outcome Metrics Using Salesforce Flows Pilot
